SHORT="CCC creates user defined cd-rom covers"
cat << EOF
CCC is a commandline tool which creates user defined cd-rom covers by
generating latex-output.
Features: User definable Title, Subtitle, Backcover and Sidetext and
support for multi-disc sets. 
EOF

